g2:c.PROCEDURE.g2:a.TEXT:
_g2com-rpc-post-message(val: value)
begin inform the operator that "[val]"; end

g2:c.FREE-TEXT.g2:a.TEXT: g2com-start-over-interface(ComName: text, ComArguments: item-or-value, InterfaceClass: symbol)
declare remote G2COM-call(text, all remaining item-or-value ) = (all remaining item-or-value)
declare remote G2COM-start(text, all remaining item-or-value ) = ()

g2:c.REMOTE-PROCEDURE-DECLARATION.g2:a.TEXT: declare remote G2COM-call(text, all remaining (item-or-value including the system attributes : name of item, current value of variable-or-parameter,uuid,foundation-class, g2-user-mode )) = (all remaining item-or-value)
declare remote G2COM-start(text, all remaining ( item-or-value including the system attributes : name of item, current value of variable-or-parameter, uuid, foundation-class, g2-user-mode ))=()

g2:c.PROCEDURE.g2:a.TEXT: _g2item_refresh(x : text ) = (item-or-value) begin if there exists an item q such that( the uuid of q = x) then begin return q end; return -1 end

_g2item_delete(x:text, classname:symbol) = (integer) begin if there exists an item q such that( the uuid of q = x and the class of q = classname) then begin delete q without permanence checks; return 0 end ; return -1 end

_g2item_subscribe(txtUUID : text, callback: symbol, towhat : text, atOrList : value, userData : value) = (value) subit : class item ; iHndl : integer ; horhs : value; erobj : class error; ermsg : text ; cbn : class procedure = __g2com_selection_event; ifo : class gsi-interface; begin if there exists an item subit such that (the uuid of subit = txtUUID) then begin if towhat = "DELETE" then begin iHndl = call g2-subscribe-to-item-deletion(subit, callback, userData) ; return iHndl end else if towhat ="MODIFY" then begin horhs = call g2-subscribe-to-item-attributes(subit, atOrList, callback, userData) ; return horhs end else if towhat="COLORCHANGE" then begin iHndl = call g2-subscribe-to-item-color-pattern-change(subit, callback, userData); return iHndl end else if towhat="CUSTOM" then begin iHndl = call g2-subscribe-to-custom-event(subit, atOrList, callback, userData) ; return iHndl end else if towhat="WKSPC-ITEM_ADDED" and subit is a kb-workspace then begin iHndl = call g2-subscribe-to-add-item-to-workspace(subit, callback, userData) ; return iHndl end else if towhat="WKSPC-ITEM_DEL" and subit is a kb-workspace then begin iHndl = call g2-subscribe-to-remove-item-from-workspace(subit, callback, userData) ; return iHndl end else if towhat ="VALUE" then begin if subit is a variable or subit is a parameter then begin iHndl = call g2-subscribe-to-variable-or-parameter-value(subit, callback, userData) ; return iHndl end else return "Item is not a variable or parameter" end else if towhat ="SELECTION" then begin if subit is a g2-window then begin ifo = call g2-current-remote-interface () ; iHndl = call g2-ui-register-selection-callback (the symbol SELECTION-CHANGED,cbn,userData,subit) ; if iHndl > 0 then start g2-set-hash-table-value(_g2com-selection-hash-table, iHndl, ifo) ; return iHndl end else return "Item is not a window" end else return -1 end else return -1 end on error (erobj) ermsg = "[the text of the error-description of erobj]"; delete erobj ; return ermsg end

_g2com-bad-version(axlver : text) = () localVer : text ; begin localVer = call _g2com_kb_ver() ; post "*VERSION MISMATCH* ActiveXLInk requires version [axlver] of G2Com.kb. The loaded G2Com.kb has version [localVer]." end

_g2com-referenced-item(uuidin:text)=(item-or-value) origit : class item ; begin if there exists an item origit such that ( the uuid of origit = uuidin) then return origit else return the symbol none end

g2:c.REMOTE-PROCEDURE-DECLARATION.g2:a.TEXT: declare remote _G2COM-trigger-selection-event(integer, (item-or-value including the system attributes : name of item, current value of variable-or-parameter, uuid, g2-user-mode ))= ()

g2:c.PROCEDURE.g2:a.TEXT:
twaxl-close-tw-connection (win: class g2-window)
begin system call g2-system-command(the symbol close-telewindows-connection, win, win, the symbol none) end

twaxl-show-workspace-with-name(session-id: integer, hwnd-hi: integer, hwnd-low:integer, workspace-name: text) begin system call twaxl-show-workspace-with-name(session-id, hwnd-hi, hwnd-low, workspace-name); end

twaxl-show-workspace-with-uuid(session-id: integer, hwnd-hi: integer, hwnd-low:integer, workspace-uuid: text) begin system call twaxl-show-workspace-with-uuid(session-id, hwnd-hi, hwnd-low, workspace-uuid); end
